{"tid":2453223,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"30歲白人唔夠阿婆打，反被打爆碙瞓低送院","createTime":"2021-03-19T10:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T10:40:50.000Z","uid":49648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d1686e23c41598ce0c9bbbe6587dd62de100b732","tid":2453223,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:25:21.000Z","msg":"美國有亞裔阿婆無故被白人男子打　　該名男子卻被打到瞓低要送院<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/DennisKPIX/status/1372241168663076864?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1372241168663076864%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_c10&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2021%2F03%2Feldery-asian-woman-got-hit-but-the-guy-injured-even-more%2F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDennisKPIX%2Fstatus%2F1372241168663076864%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1372241168663076864%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_c10%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.winandmac.com%252F2021%252F03%252Feldery-asian-woman-got-hit-but-the-guy-injured-even-more%252F&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=ba72c68f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDennisKPIX%2Fstatus%2F1372241168663076864%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1372241168663076864%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_c10%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.winandmac.com%252F2021%252F03%252Feldery-asian-woman-got-hit-but-the-guy-injured-even-more%252F&h=1b46cecf\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/DennisKPIX/status/1372241168663076864?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1372241168663076864%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_c10&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2021%2F03%2Feldery-asian-woman-got-hit-but-the-guy-injured-even-more%2F</a><br />\n<br />\n因為武漢肺炎的關係，美國針對亞裔的種族歧視攻擊個案爆升。在當地時間今星期三（17號），於美國三藩市Market Street發生一單個案，一名70多歲的亞裔阿婆無情情被30多歲男子攻擊。結果，雖然阿婆都有受傷，但該名白人男子竟然被打到瞓低，除了臉上爆血外，還受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n阿婆疑似用台山話又或者廣東話，指住男子大罵為什麼要無情情打她。她情緒仍然十分激動，並不停向在場的途人和警察指，這名男子突然攻擊她。據稱，當時阿婆只係依靠住一條燈柱，然後這名男子就無情情攻擊她。當地警察暫時未知該名男子為什麼要打阿婆，亦不確定是否與阿婆的膚色有關。"},{"pid":"13d53686023a4a5e189290b7d7e23cdaf205e8df","tid":2453223,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:26:20.000Z","msg":"碙係正字？"},{"pid":"c2dda5219c93770640d3a2f732610733e30c985b","tid":2453223,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:40:50.000Z","msg":"好撚渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}